description: The OPPO Find N2 Flip’s striking folding design is exquisitely created to pure precision with its true gapless finish, Available in Astral Black and Moonlit Purple. OPPO’s first Flip boasts the industry’s largest 3.26” vertical cover screen. Perfect for quick text replies, answering calls and snapping high resolution 50MP selfies all while the phone is closed for ultimate efficiency. Open Find N2 Flip between 40-135° to activate FlexForm Mode, allowing for creative photography or video capture and productive video meetings. When flipped open, Find N2 Flip boasts a smooth full screen user experience across the 6.8” display. With the industry leading flexion hinge, Find N2 Flip sits flush when closed and is certified by TUV Rheinland for superior folding reliability compared to the competition. And while your hinge will keep on flipping, your battery will keep on going with the largest battery capacity EVER in a flip smartphone at 4300mAh and with SUPERVOOC charging technology built in, just 15-minutes will rejuvenate to 34%.
